The gun does have an aggressive feel. It's comfortable, and grips well, point of aim and impact great. Very accurate groups, fast follow up shots. Need to control the gun like a man. It is a .45ACP. Badass.


Available for FTF in Longview/Tyler area. Otherwise I will ship nationwide for $20.00 to your FFL!

Thanks for looking!
